Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓抑高昂的鼓動 奔向暮色昏暗的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心和客套之間 對那傢伙的想法複雜交錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有答案也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這份愛粉身碎骨 你的表情為何如此寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謊言 心機 嫉妒 背叛 有如家常便飯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須大驚小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃之心點燃火苗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想再去見你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不行動 何時才要做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇花開 薔薇花落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心中有我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅的 優美的 華麗的飛舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇花開 薔薇花飛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼中有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心祈禱的話 一定能改變命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活得燦爛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17話 死之宣告！墮天掌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傷口是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗曹家拳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三國時代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫家，曹家，劉家三分天下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護他們所成立的教派
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是靈王，芒狂雲\N和我所繼承的北斗孫家拳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其絕招是改變人體的內力之氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進而自在操縱的“操氣術”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你看看這傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是被剛硬的指力所刺穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這男的是我很信任的秘書
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗殺的目標一定是我沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在死前說了一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校你要小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個男的會操縱人腦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，隨意操縱人腦的拳法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅華會少幫主\N北斗曹家拳，張太炎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗之拳可是高深莫測的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要單靠指上功夫去達到神的領域\N這是非常困難的修練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要在這塊大陸上\N去面對更多更強的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗曹家拳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變得如何呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:04:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了\N反正這下子就不用怕閻王了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再狠狠教訓基斯一頓\N我要再次和紅華會享受風花雪月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之前先解決蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要先收拾掉蘇菲才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我會有生命危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時差一點就能成功了\N結果被基斯破壞我的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在那之後就把蘇菲藏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事不宜遲，要把蘇菲找出來…\N把事情做個了斷才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是基斯上校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一小隊看守中庭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二第三小隊負責醫院內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然太炎回來上海了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難預料他會耍什麼手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅華會是真心想從\N青幫的手上奪回上海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他第一個找你開刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕下一個目標就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，問題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們身邊的人…北大路和蘇菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再後退一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪種傷患都能安全運送喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感謝租界警察的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校這邊也討好一下\N萬一紅華會掛了還有退路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是要運哪位呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美麗的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們來檢查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我給找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來她躲在那裡，好機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，先把蘇菲移到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，今晚就出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護衛就交給軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了掩人耳目，請你留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都聽到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘇菲這是飛蛾撲火啊，太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去確認女人的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，射出的子彈全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，這次一定會成功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孫家拳只有護身術的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法撐太久的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你應該要再多練練才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真會說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閻王…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是紅華會吧\N不然怎麼會認得出我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺平了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還有紅華會餘黨的內奸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經送到內院的病房了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳志郎，拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去協助北大路的侍衛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，但問題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內奸究竟是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子別躲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘇菲我找到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人跑去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下\N我聽說她記憶開始恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她肯定會回去那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳回來啦，蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不必再擔心受怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看看，這裡是妳成長的家園
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路上辛苦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到上海就安全無虞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，因為這裡是桃源鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃源鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯\N就像妳從歐洲逃亡過來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後會出現更多流連失所的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要建立一個新國度\N收留那些無家可歸的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都不受任何約束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃源鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我安身立命的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的夏洛洛哥哥正為此而奔忙着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，哥哥在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說要來接我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想介紹一個人給他認識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你見見一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的愛人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我最心愛最重要的人，彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，哥哥，聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:15:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我和這個人…\N已經有了小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跑去哪裡了，小蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出來，小蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那時殺了彼得的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳的記憶都恢復了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳不恢復記憶\N活着像個洋娃娃倒還安全
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把妳連同那些記憶一起毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在抓我的頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對別人的記憶有意見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對記憶有意見的話就衝着我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閻王！為什麼你會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尋着你殘留在墊子上的臭味來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會飛得高高的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你識相，送你飛上天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我點了你的經絡秘孔\N解啞門天聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來，不管什麼\N你都會誠實回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我，你為什麼要殺蘇菲？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，我沒…我沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些和紅華會有勾結的人\N都把基斯視為眼中釘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要綁架他妹妹蘇菲\N就可以威脅他離開上海了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，為了追捕他們兩人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一路追到這裡\N不小心就把彼得…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了，不用說下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，請讓我全數坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡…在這裡殺了彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她因為過於震驚\N而喪失了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你不要再說下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會帶妳去找妳哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開快一點，馬上去陸軍醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳志郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都聽說了\N包括馬爾羅的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙我已經解決掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快去見你妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的，真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄，請留步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你！我們是不是見過面？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上有和我一樣的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相同的氣味嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的表情好猙獰喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心你這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會沒人愛喔，閻王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在報紙上看到你跟紅華會幹架
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N我探病之後還要趕着去葬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲，蘇菲\N哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.27,0:22:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲，妳想起來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳認得我是哥哥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，我好想你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的記憶真的恢復了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳等一下，我現在就上去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你不用急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪裡都不會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.07,0:22:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的兄妹重逢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就輪到葬禮的開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:22:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門上面有那小子的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的直覺告訴我\N要趕快逃離這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝化甘油的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是定時炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.34,0:23:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛會使人盲目
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.32,0:24:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們道上最危險的一種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真該早點提醒他們才對的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧，基斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.21,0:24:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，對不起\N我們好不容易才重逢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死，蘇菲妳要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.38,0:24:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥會建立新的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.21,0:24:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立爸媽和妳都夢寐以求\N不受任何迫害的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.02,0:24:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.52,0:24:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.82,0:24:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是彼得在等我了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.86,0:24:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢用這種臉去見他…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.24,0:25:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看見了嗎？妳看…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.21,0:25:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很美喔，蘇菲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.48,0:25:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想介紹他給哥哥認識喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.77,0:25:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在瞪我，那傢伙居然沒死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.48,0:25:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.64,0:25:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剝下紅華會的假面具\N露出魔獸的真面目之後
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.55,0:25:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會害怕的人是他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.42,0:25:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本好吃懶做的北斗神拳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.62,0:25:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我用這雙手終結他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.89,0:25:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死之宣告“墮天掌”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.13,0:25:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來他身上所散發的是\N北斗曹家拳的魔性氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.95,0:26:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種血肉之軀的疼痛\N怎麼比得上…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.99,0:26:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂黯然凋落的那種哀傷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.69,0:26:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓你嚐嚐那個滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.34,0:26:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們用純真無邪的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.88,0:26:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆相視而笑的Sweet Days
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.78,0:26:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街景已不復以往
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.92,0:26:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在我倆仍相伴左右
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.29,0:26:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是未來的際遇卻很難說
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.06,0:27:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連老天爺都無法捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.00,0:27:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融進迎面吹來的風裡walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.01,0:27:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數顆future之星
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.54,0:27:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜悄悄的被鑲在無涯的天空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.38,0:27:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交疊的溫熱維繫着一切閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.02,0:27:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充斥着無法實現的諾言
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.99,0:27:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界漸漸沉淪墮落
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.19,0:27:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kissing till l die
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.83,0:27:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力掩蓋傷痕 創造永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.60,0:27:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在危機之中讓我們相愛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.27,0:27:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So，也許是我倆的生存方式come on！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
